snippet.textDisplay: This just IS NOT KASHMIRI MUSIC… Using Kashmiri lyrics and mashing up something from here and there is a sheer insult to our authentic Kashmiri folk/Sufi music… Putting pun on wazwaan part and then wanwun mash up without that second compulsory repetition as is in actual wanwun, that too with blaring western musical instruments is just noise and nothing else. Why are we westernizing ourselves? Why can’t we stick to our authenticity? Are we feeling shame of being our TRUE SELF & proud to be copy cats??
